This module implements MultiHash. Supported hashes are:

  1. IDENTITY
  2. SHA2-256/SHA2-512
  3. DBL-SHA2-256
  4. SHA3/KECCAK
  5. SHAKE-128/SHAKE-256
  6. BLAKE2s/BLAKE2s
  7. SHA1

Hashes which are not yet supported

  1. SKEIN
  2. MURMUR
